➜这个东北小伙制作的黑白片，引爆动画业的夏天
http://www.sohu.com/a/411278911_157906	47499
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=207917838&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200803/819cf125e5304fcaa269a08f4434309f.gif" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">无声、黑白、定格动画——</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">短片《风雨廊桥》包含了许多“小众元素”，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然而一上线就被好评刷爆，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">目前豆瓣评分8.9、B站9.8。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200803/5f619fcf86484a56b31d229a21591545.gif" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">故事发生在唐末乱世，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">年迈的老侠客在廊桥上，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">遇到对一名小女孩图谋不轨的官兵和强盗，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">老人本可选择自保，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">却依然对两人举刀相向。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
